Subject: VirtualBox Problem (Orbit)
Description:
Hello,  
We installed VirtualBox on our client’s machine and successfully imported the .ovf file. We configured the IP settings correctly and can ping the machine. However, we are unable to access the web panel. What could be the reason for this?
What_We_Know__c: Nginx was not running because it ran into dhparam error
Solution_Comment__c: ran a dhparam command and the service was running ok
